flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Receive User Message]
    B --> C{Heuristic Check<br/>Travel-related?}
    C -->|No| R1[Reject with<br/>Off-topic Message]
    C -->|Yes| D[LLM Judge<br/>Topic Validation]
    D --> E{LLM Verdict<br/>Travel-related?}
    E -->|No| R2[Reject with<br/>Off-topic Message]
    E -->|Yes| F[Forward to<br/>Travel Advisor LLM]
    F --> G[Generate Travel<br/>Advice Response]
    G --> H[Return Response<br/>to User]
    R1 --> I{Continue<br/>Conversation?}
    R2 --> I
    H --> I
    I -->|Yes| B
    I -->|No| Z([End])